622
00:37:06,630 --> 00:37:07,550
Just put it here.

623
00:37:07,550 --> 00:37:08,000
Sure.

624
00:37:08,710 --> 00:37:09,310
Thank you.

625
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,460
Have a good rest, Miss Xin.

626
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:25,900
