652
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:50,960
Fine then.

653
00:38:52,230 --> 00:38:53,150
Drink this.

654
00:38:53,710 --> 00:38:54,640
We'll proceed to

655
00:38:54,880 --> 00:38:56,540
